<h2>Bus Route Overview</h2>

<p>The scenic mountain bus route from Tobu Nikko Station to Yumoto Onsen takes approximately <strong>1 hour 20-25 minutes</strong> and climbs through stunning landscapes including Lake Chuzenji, Kegon Falls, Ryuzu Falls, and the Senjogahara Plateau. The bus operates frequently throughout the day on the Nikko-Yumoto line.</p>

<div class="highlight">
<strong>Bus Service Details</strong><br>
• <strong>Operator:</strong> Tobu Bus Nikko<br>
• <strong>One-way fare:</strong> ¥1,950 (or free with Nikko All Area Pass)<br>
• <strong>Frequency:</strong> Every 30-60 minutes during peak season<br>
• <strong>Journey time:</strong> 80-85 minutes<br>
• <strong>Route:</strong> Tobu Nikko Station → Shinkyo → Chuzenji Onsen → Ryuzu Falls → Yumoto Onsen
</div>

