<h2>How to Purchase Bus Tickets on iPhone</h2>

<h3>Option 1: Digital Bus Pass (Recommended)</h3>

<p>Purchase the <strong>Tobu Bus Yumoto Onsen Pass</strong> through your iPhone for maximum convenience:</p>

<ol>
<li>Visit <a href="https://ticket.jorudan.co.jp/tobu-bus-nikko/en/" target="_blank">Jorudan Mobile Tickets - Tobu Bus Nikko</a> on your iPhone</li>
<li>Select <strong>"Tobu Bus Yumoto Onsen Pass"</strong> (¥3,500 for 2 days unlimited rides)</li>
<li>Choose your starting date (October 12 or whenever you first use it)</li>
<li>Complete payment with your credit card</li>
<li>Receive the digital pass on your phone immediately</li>
<li>When boarding: Show the colorful bar code screen to the driver along with your numbered ticket from the machine</li>
</ol>

<div class="highlight">
<strong>Jorudan Mobile Pass Benefits</strong><br>
• No physical ticket pickup required<br>
• Activate instantly from your phone<br>
• Covers Nikko Station ↔ Yumoto Onsen unlimited for 2 days<br>
