<h3>Option 2: Use Your Nikko All Area Pass</h3>

<p>If you purchased the <strong>Nikko All Area Pass</strong> for your train journey (recommended in the train card), it already includes unlimited bus rides to Yumoto Onsen! Simply show your pass to the driver when boarding and exiting. No additional ticket needed.</p>

<h3>Option 3: Pay Single Fares</h3>

<p>If traveling without a pass, you can pay per ride:</p>

<ol>
<li>Board the bus from the <strong>rear door</strong></li>
<li>Take a numbered ticket from the machine by the door</li>
<li>When your stop approaches, press the stop button</li>
<li>Check the fare display board at the front (match your ticket number to the fare)</li>
<li>Exit from the <strong>front door</strong> and pay the driver (¥1,950 cash or IC card like Suica/PASMO)</li>
</ol>

